Imane Abdelahad (Arabic: , amụrụ na 21 Julaị 1994) bụ onye Morocco na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-edebe goolu maka  Egwuregwu  Casablanca na otu ụmụ nwanyị nke Morocco.
Abdelahad gbara bọọlụ na 2017-18 Njikọ mbụ nke ụmụ nwanyị Turkish  oge maka Beşiktaş J.K
na-apụta na egwuregwu isii nke ọkara nke abụọ nke  otu egwuregwu
